     355E 2AAE     
0040 3560 A100                   data rambuf           ; \ i p0  = Pointer to 5 byte string buffer
0041 3562 A02C                   data uint16.unpacked  ; | i p1  = Pointer to output buffer
0042 3564 0020                   data 32               ; / i p2  = Padding char to match against
